5 LangGraph Agent Nodes

DataFetcher — pulls SEC filing, yfinance data, news in parallel
RAGRetriever — chunks + embeds filing, retrieves top-K relevant sections
SentimentAnalyzer — scores news sentiment per article, aggregates
FinancialAnalyzer — calculates derived metrics, trend direction, risk flags
ReportGenerator — Groq LLM generates structured report with Risk Score (0–100), KPI Summary, News Sentiment, Risk Factors, Analyst Verdict, Buy/Hold/Sell signal


5 Dash Dashboard Pages

Page 1 — Research: Ticker search, risk gauge, KPI cards, full LLM report, Buy/Hold/Sell badge
Page 2 — Financials: Candlestick chart, revenue bars, margin trend, P/E vs sector
Page 3 — Sentiment: Sentiment timeline, positive/negative breakdown, top headlines
Page 4 — History: SQLite-backed report table, risk score comparison, CSV export
Page 5 — Eval Metrics: FinanceBench accuracy, hallucination rate, ROUGE-L vs baseline


All API Keys Needed

